FBIS4-9247 "dreeu078__a94029" FBIS-EEU-94-078-A Daily Report 22 Apr 1994 ANNEX Bosnia-Herzegovina German TV Team Temporarily Arrested German TV Team Temporarily Arrested AU2204105794 Hamburg DPA in German 0926 GMT 22 Apr 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU2204105794 Hamburg DPA German BFN [Text] Pale/Augsburg (DPA) -- Serbian military have temporarily put a German television team of the SAT-1 private station under house arrest in the Bosnian town of Pale. On Friday morning [22 April] the journalists, who had been detained the day before, were released again, the television station announced. The two reporters are supposed to leave the country today. The television team had filmed scenes in the streets of Pale. Military officers stopped the filming and seized the technical equipment. The two journalists and their Serbian interpreter had to hand in their passports and their accreditations. They were prohibited from leaving the hotel, where they had been taken.
